fields.value:
**Normal Attack** (Night): {Don't} attack a player {but instead all their visitors} with bones and stuff.
**Special Attack** (Night): Use your special attack, roleblocking a player {every night for the rest of the game. Anyone who visits them also is permanently roleblocked. This also applies to anyone who was affected by visiting - it can spread. Unseen members are immune. 2 uses.}
**{Fake} Mercy** (Night): If you are attacked, {pretend to} offer mercy. The attacker will be told to select a new target. If they select you again, this won't activate again. {However, you will retaliate, and kill them, while you will survive.}
**Cleave** during the day. Infinite uses.
